        <section id="About_Me">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>
                I am a Ph.D. candidate in Applied Mathematics at Aix-Marseille University, France, working under the supervision of Prof. Kai Schneider and Dr. Keigo Matsuda. My research focuses on particle dynamics in fully developed turbulence, utilizing tessellation, multiresolution, and machine learning methods.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="Education">
            <h2>Education</h2>
